snippet: The blue letters over an entrance at the Trump International Hotel alluded to questions about the president’s business affairs with foreign governments.
lead_paragraph: Large blue letters projected over the entrance to the Trump International Hotel in Washington on Monday night read “Pay Trump Bribes Here,” an allusion to questions about President Trump’s business affairs with foreign governments.
